            "elType": "widget",
            "settings": {
              "html": "\n<div style=\"background:#08122A;padding:0 0 64px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.15);position:relative;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <div style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(196,154,42,0.03) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(196,154,42,0.03) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:60px 60px;pointer-events:none;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;position:relative;z-index:1;\">\n    \n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:1.8rem;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:1px;background:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\"></div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;\">Growth Stage \u00b7 6 Months</span></div>\n    <h1 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,5rem);font-weight:300;line-height:1.04;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 1.8rem;\">Built to scale.<br>Built to close.</h1>\n    <p style=\"font-size:1rem;line-height:1.7;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);max-width:600px;margin:1.5rem 0 0;\">The BMIIL Accelerator is for health and wellness startups that already have a product, early customers, or traction \u2014 and need structured, intensive support to reach the next order of magnitude.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#F7F3EC;padding:7rem 0;\">\n  <div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;\">\n\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1rem;margin-bottom:5rem;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align:center;padding:2rem;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;\"><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;\">6</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;margin-top:4px;\">Month Sprint</div></div><div style=\"text-align:center;padding:2rem;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;\"><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;\">8</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;margin-top:4px;\">Seats Available</div></div><div style=\"text-align:center;padding:2rem;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;\"><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;\">2\u00d7</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;margin-top:4px;\">Demo Days</div></div><div style=\"text-align:center;padding:2rem;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;\"><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;\">3</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;margin-top:4px;\">Focused Sprints</div></div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Is this for you -->\n    <p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">Is This For You?</p>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;margin-bottom:5rem;\">\n      <div>\n        <h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 1rem;\">\u2713 This track is built for you if\u2026</h3>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#3B6D11;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You have a health or wellness product that real customers have used</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#3B6D11;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You understand your ICP and have validated the core value proposition</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#3B6D11;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You're looking to raise your first institutional round \u2014 angel, pre-seed, or seed</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#3B6D11;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You want to access hospital systems, pharma companies, or healthcare corporates as B2B partners</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#3B6D11;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You need structured support with GTM, revenue operations, or channel partnerships</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 1rem;\">\u2717 Consider a different track if\u2026</h3>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#A32D2D;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2717</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You're still building your first prototype \u2014 the Medtech Incubation track will serve you better</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#A32D2D;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2717</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">Your product is primarily an Ayurveda or traditional medicine innovation</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#A32D2D;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2717</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You haven't yet identified a clear monetisation model or target customer segment</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#A32D2D;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2717</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">Your primary challenge is technical development, not growth or fundraising</span></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Sprints -->\n    <p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">Sprint Structure</p>\n    <h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:300;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 2.5rem;\">Six months. Three focused sprints.</h2>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.5rem;margin-bottom:5rem;\">\n      <div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <div style=\"background:#08122A;padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;\">\n    <div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;margin-bottom:4px;\">Sprint 1 \u00b7 Month 1</div>\n    <div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:#FFFFFF;\">Diagnosis & Positioning</div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:1.5rem;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:#4A5C78;margin:0 0 1rem;\">An honest, structured audit of where you actually are. We stress-test your product, market understanding, team, and financials before building any growth plan.</p>\n    <div style=\"border-top:1px solid #EDE8DE;padding-top:1rem;\"><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Business model audit & P&L review</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 ICP validation & customer segmentation</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Competitive positioning map</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Fundraising readiness scorecard</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 6-month OKR framework defined</div></div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n      <div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <div style=\"background:#08122A;padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;\">\n    <div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;margin-bottom:4px;\">Sprint 2 \u00b7 Months 2\u20134</div>\n    <div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:#FFFFFF;\">Growth & GTM Execution</div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:1.5rem;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:#4A5C78;margin:0 0 1rem;\">Full execution sprint. Three months of structured growth activities \u2014 go-to-market, distribution, pilot partnerships, revenue operations, and investor pipeline.</p>\n    <div style=\"border-top:1px solid #EDE8DE;padding-top:1rem;\"><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 GTM campaigns live</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 3+ hospital or corporate pilots</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Revenue ops system built</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Investor pipeline of 20+</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Mid-program demo day</div></div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n      <div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <div style=\"background:#08122A;padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;\">\n    <div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;margin-bottom:4px;\">Sprint 3 \u00b7 Months 5\u20136</div>\n    <div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:#FFFFFF;\">Fundraise & Scale</div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:1.5rem;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:#4A5C78;margin:0 0 1rem;\">The final sprint is built around one outcome \u2014 closing capital. Investor deck refined, data room ready, term sheets negotiated.</p>\n    <div style=\"border-top:1px solid #EDE8DE;padding-top:1rem;\"><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Investor deck (final)</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Data room complete</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Demo Day pitch</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Term sheet negotiations</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Post-cohort investor introductions</div></div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"background:#08122A;border-radius:4px;padding:3rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:2rem;\">\n      <div><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:300;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 0.5rem;\">Ready to apply for the Accelerator?</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);margin:0;\">Applications are rolling. We spend more time with early applicants.</p></div>\n      <a href=\"/apply/\" style=\"background:#C49A2A;color:#08122A;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:2px;text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap;\">Apply for This Track \u2192</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>"
            },
            "elements": [],
            "widgetType": "html"
          }
        ],
        "isInner": false
      }
